a9a873f2b0209c684bcc97a74558b0e.mp4?t=1722274965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016080/extras/getToWorkStep.png?t=1722274965\" /></span><br><br>To fund his dreams, Slime takes up all kinds of job offers.<br>From <i>investigating the disappearance of a cult leader in a bottomless pit</i>, to a relaxing afternoon trimming the hedges of an overgrown flower garden...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016080/extras/399edc9fc2294f34e48b4d7bf89bd63b.poster.avif?t=1722274965\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016080/extras/399edc9fc2294f34e48b4d7bf89bd63b.webm?t=1722274965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016080/extras/399edc9fc2294f34e48b4d7bf89bd63b.mp4?t=1722274965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016080/extras/e467794666908f425959848bf4898dd9.avif?t=1722274965\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>Reap the sweet rewards!<br><br>Use your hard-earned money to splurge on house accessories, access secret worlds, and snatch those - really, like <strong><i>REALLY</i></strong> cool sunglasses™.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016080/extras/c22e68b79a77b6386b3c231beabd359a.poster.avif?t=1722274965\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016080/extras/c22e68b79a77b6386b3c231beabd359a.webm?t=1722274965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\